{"tid":1583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家入一入黎睇睇","createTime":"2016-11-25T16:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T15:34:08.000Z","uid":8644,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2958eac55f0b35c63ca6ca8c5b82b504d599005c","tid":1583,"uid":8644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T16:38:33.000Z","msg":"請大家容許我係呢個post講感受<br />\n可能打得1999，唔滿意或者唔同意<br />\n任大家屌，我只想係度認真下<br />\n<br />\n高登成功，唔係條林早洩條仆街管理得好，而係靠一大班高質會員，佢地既創意同知識，的確令小弟係度有唔少回憶同得益<br />\n<br />\n再者高登仔可以係高登創造出高登文化，係呢度一樣可以，小弟希望大家要齊心團結，最緊要唔好善忘就得！<br />\n一樣可以創造出lihkg文化（當然唔係小圈子、5p同5毛）<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲繼續發揮高登文化<br />\n係度繼續出高質post吸引更多高登果邊啲人過黎<br />\n等東張西望都訪問連尼住巴打！落鳩條仆街早洩面<br />\n幫plus仔爭番口氣"},{"pid":"ee89384194a82e23db6d968e8b7300e8cc549e46","tid":1583,"uid":8644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T16:48:49.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"bf6531b340fd52caeb0c0b80de450c46735027ad","tid":1583,"uid":8644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"十連"},{"pid":"2c9e0d30b9aff1b80dc6d2f88fb1a760d48ec6f2","tid":1583,"uid":8644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T16:55:31.000Z","msg":"十連"},{"pid":"7db63ce5cffcdd77939ad738f7d45b7646f03286","tid":1583,"uid":8644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T16:58:06.000Z","msg":"十連"},{"pid":"9ff78d048d5e4e2457d2a79478d2a3c12f1858db","tid":1583,"uid":8644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:33:15.000Z","msg":"十連"},{"pid":"6ffe55bbf98769cabd059b497bdd1de97d1c75dd","tid":1583,"uid":8644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T17:33:25.000Z","msg":"慢慢十連"},{"pid":"c47b03cd1ce35e903d0fd9f76d5afe99592e3c50","tid":1583,"uid":8644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T18:13:43.000Z","msg":"無人理"},{"pid":"32c64caef1257a86da79760dc1de30c55de3720b","tid":1583,"uid":2562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T1